==English==

===Etymology===
Old English ''[[hrycg]]''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#the [[line]] along which two [[sloping]] [[surface]]s [[meet]] which [[diverge]] towards the ground
#a chain of [[hills]] or [[mountains]]
#a long narrow [[elevation]] on an [[ocean]] [[bottom]]

